F_s(\xi)
f(x)
f(x)=1/x
F_s(\xi) = \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}\int_0^\infty f(x)\sin(\xi x)\text{d}x.
f(x)=\sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}\int_0^\infty F_s(\xi)\sin(\xi x)\text{d}\xi.
F_s(\xi) = \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}\int_0^\infty \frac{\sin(\xi x)}{x}\text{d}x = \sqrt{\frac{\pi}{2}}.
f(x) = \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}\int_0^\infty\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{2}}\sin(\xi x)\text{d}\xi=\int_0^\infty\sin(\xi x)\text{d}\xi,
f(x)=1/x
x \to \frac{1}{x}
